{"tid":977113,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【後悔去PSG】尼馬曾5次致電巴塞想歸隊","createTime":"2019-01-11T02:54:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T03:24:41.000Z","uid":147522,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4297793a5840d95b0d3fb39537b90a0cd2d23f07","tid":977113,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T02:54:41.000Z","msg":"　　西班牙媒體《馬卡報》援引《世界體育報》的消息，尼馬對於轉會巴黎聖日耳門感到後悔，曾五次致電巴塞，希望能夠重返魯營球場。<br />\n<br />\n　　該報透露，尼馬渴望重返巴塞，他的經理人也是他的父親出面，直接跟巴塞主席貝圖美奧對話，希望能將尼馬帶回巴塞。《世界體育報》曝光了尼馬父親對貝圖美奧的那段話：「他很失望，他感到很抱歉。」<br />\n<br />\n　　據悉，尼馬相信巴黎聖日耳門缺少競技體育計劃。尼馬於2017年夏天離開巴塞，以2.22億歐元的高價加盟巴黎聖日耳門。"},{"pid":"6cdb171c059102d5bfa7cb806cb3961f55984953","tid":977113,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T03:02:52.000Z","msg":"《馬卡報》援引《世界體育報》"},{"pid":"b8bac4b3558bd2d2538fc506ff4737708b2cc43e","tid":977113,"uid":3747,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"6cdb171c059102d5bfa7cb806cb3961f55984953","tid":977113,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T03:02:52.000Z","msg":"《馬卡報》援引《世界體育報》"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T03:05:29.000Z","msg":"兩份垃圾"},{"pid":"40e27c57194e3e84a800ccfa643d154ffcfae396","tid":977113,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T03:09:24.000Z","msg":"去下體會好過啦"},{"pid":"972b968924fc37941a917f40825ac9f33e6b60cc","tid":977113,"uid":141519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T03:13:23.000Z","msg":"鐘聲響起歸家的訊號"},{"pid":"36d1ee9615352e43553b39f7f241dcef37481b8c","tid":977113,"uid":82304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T03:13:39.000Z","msg":"go man la diu"},{"pid":"f32035a7637959fe2b44597ae932f8c71b40ffb8","tid":977113,"uid":166785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T03:14:39.000Z","msg":"賣走古仔應該夠比"},{"pid":"170e7696da2e85dcece5d47bb4b407a12d883c39","tid":977113,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20